text: Auchay-sur-Vendée is a commune in the department of Vendée, western France. The municipality was established on 1 January 2017 by merger of the former communes of Auzay (the seat) and Chaix.Arrêté préfectoral 4 August 2016 == See also == *Communes of the Vendée department == References == Category:Communes of Vendée Category:States and territories established in 2017
title: Auchay-sur-Vendée
